overview:
Texas Electricity Choice is a free online resource which helps homeowners and businesses in the deregulated Texas electricity market locate the lowest Texas electricity rates from the best Texas electricity providers.

At TexasElectricityChoice.com, Texas electricity providers compete against each other in order to win your business by offering their best Texas electricity rates and plans. Whether you are looking for a low fixed rate, prepaid electricity, or 100% green energy, Texas Electricity Choice has just the right plan for you!
